Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with parameterized linear temporal logic and its model checking.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper presents an algorithm to determine optimal variable valuations in games.
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is relevant as the paper deals with graph games and winning conditions.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper presents algorithms for solving games.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper deals with temporal operators and their use in specifications.
